# Production manifest for Snakefile
# Columns (tab-separated, no required header, # lines ignored):
#
#   sample        KN_BC       bam_path             arrays_path       [mode]
#
# sample      — unique identifier for this pool / KN_BC combination
# KN_BC       — Kinnex barcode (e.g. bcM0003)
# bam_path    — path to pre-Skera CCS/HiFi BAM
# arrays_path — path to arrays file for this run (may be a master file
#               covering all KN_BCs on the SMRT Cell; the pipeline subsets
#               by KN_BC automatically)
# mode        — OPTIONAL 5th column: "single" or "multi"
#               Overrides auto-detection. Omit to let the pipeline decide
#               based on library count in the arrays file.
#
# ── Mode auto-detection ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# When the mode column is absent, the pipeline counts libraries sharing this
# KN_BC in the arrays file:
#   1 library  → SINGLE-LIBRARY (Skera BAM passed directly as HIGH_CONF)
#   >1 library → MULTI-LIBRARY  (full Bayesian array assignment pipeline)
# The detected mode is logged at startup so the decision is always visible.
#
# ── Mode override cross-validation ──────────────────────────────────────────
# mode=multi, 1 library found   → WARNING, proceeds through assignment path
# mode=single, 1 library found  → proceeds as single-library (agrees)
# mode=multi, >1 libraries found → proceeds as multi-library (agrees)
# mode=single, >1 libraries found → ERROR (library name is ambiguous)
#
# ── Mixed-mode example ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# The following lines show a SMRT Cell with 4 KN_BCs:
#   - bcM0003 and bcM0004 have 2 libraries each → MULTI-LIBRARY (auto)
#   - bcM0005 has 1 library                     → SINGLE-LIBRARY (auto)
#   - bcM0006 has 1 library but forced to multi  → MULTI-LIBRARY (override)
#
# Pool001_bcM0003	bcM0003	/path/to/Pool001.ccs.bam	arrays/SmrtCell01_master.txt
# Pool001_bcM0004	bcM0004	/path/to/Pool001.ccs.bam	arrays/SmrtCell01_master.txt
# Pool001_bcM0005	bcM0005	/path/to/Pool001.ccs.bam	arrays/SmrtCell01_master.txt
# Pool001_bcM0006	bcM0006	/path/to/Pool001.ccs.bam	arrays/SmrtCell01_master.txt	multi
